# picopico.me Project Structure Guide

This is an Astro-based personal website and blog with MDX support, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and React components.

## Key Files & Directories

### Configuration Files
- [astro.config.mjs](mdc:astro.config.mjs) - Main Astro configuration with integrations and plugins
- [src/site.config.ts](mdc:src/site.config.ts) - Site-wide settings (title, navigation, themes, social links)
- [src/content.config.ts](mdc:src/content.config.ts) - Content collections schema definitions
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript config with path aliases
- [prettier.config.js](mdc:prettier.config.js) - Code formatting rules

### Core Directory Structure
- `src/pages/` - Astro file-based routing
  - [src/pages/index.astro](mdc:src/pages/index.astro) - Homepage
  - `src/pages/posts/[slug].astro` - Individual blog posts
  - `src/pages/posts/[...page].astro` - Blog listing with pagination
  - `src/pages/tags/[tag]/[...page].astro` - Tag-based post filtering
  - `src/pages/social-cards/[slug].png.ts` - OG image generation
  - `src/pages/rss.xml.ts` - RSS feed generation

- `src/content/` - Content management with collections
  - `src/content/posts/` - Blog posts (.md/.mdx files)
  - `src/content/works/` - Portfolio/work items
  - [src/content/home.md](mdc:src/content/home.md) - Homepage content
  - [src/content/addendum.md](mdc:src/content/addendum.md) - Additional content section

- `src/components/` - UI components (mainly .astro, some .tsx for React)
- `src/layouts/` - Page layout templates
- `src/plugins/` - Custom Remark/Rehype plugins
- `src/styles/` - Global styles and Tailwind configuration

### Path Aliases (from tsconfig.json)
- `@components/*` → `src/components/*`
- `@layouts/*` → `src/layouts/*`
- `@types` → `src/types`
- `@content` → `src/content.config`
- `@utils` → `src/utils`

### Technology Stack
- **Framework**: Astro 5.x with static site generation
- **Language**: TypeScript (strict mode)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4
- **Content**: MDX with math support (KaTeX), code highlighting (Expressive Code)
- **Search**: Pagefind for client-side search
- **Icons**: Astro Icon integration
- **Fonts**: JetBrains Mono Variable
